<h1>Approve an Access Token</h1> 
</p>

<div class="row">
	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;"><p>
		<b>API Platform Base Path:</b>
		<h3><p>https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}</p></h3>
		<b>API Resource Path:</b>
		<p>/oauth2/accesstokens/{access_token}?action=approve</p>
		<p>
		
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;">
		<p>
		<b>Verb:</b>
		<span class="verb-GET">GET</span>
		</p>
		<b>Auth:</b>
		Basic Auth
		</p>


	</div>
</div>

<div class="span18">
	<p>
	
	</p>

	<b>cURL:</b>
	<pre>curl -u myname:mypass https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{myorg}/oauth2/accesstokens/{accesstoken}?action=approve</pre>



<b>Sample Response:</b> 
	<pre>Success 204

</pre>



	<b>Errors</b> 
		<pre>Failure 404 with proper error message
&lt;Error&gt;
&lt;Code&gt;keymanagement.service.invalid_accesstoken&lt;/Code&gt;
&lt;Message&gt;Invalid Access Token&lt;/Message&gt;
&lt;Contexts/&gt;
&lt;/Error&gt;

Error Codes:
1. keymanagement.service.application_not_approved
2. keymanagement.service.invalid_access_token
3. keymanagement.service.access_token_approve_failed</pre>

</div>


            </div>
        </div><!--/row-->
